      <title>巴尔金表示美联储无需急于降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-08/fed-doesn-t-need-to-be-in-a-hurry-to-cut-rates-barkin-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里士满联邦储备银行行长托马斯·巴尔金(Thomas Barkin)在讨论美国通胀和就业数据时表示，美联储在降息方面“有一些时间保持耐心”。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-08/fed-doesn-t-need-to-be-in-a-hurry-to-cut-rates-barkin-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 13:50:09 GMT</pubDate>
