    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着收益率小幅上涨，股票期货在反弹后波动：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市上涨推动市场创下历史新高后，股指期货出现波动。由于交易员准备出售 250 亿美元的 30 年期债券，美国国债收益率小幅走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 23:11:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在艾格与佩尔茨对峙之前，迪士尼公布了强劲的业绩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/disney-earnings-top-estimates-as-cost-cuts-parks-deliver-gains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华特迪士尼公司公布的第一财季盈利好于预期，并发布了乐观的全年利润前景，这为首席执行官鲍勃·艾格(Bob Iger)在今年春季的股东大会上扭转代理权挑战提供了弹药。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/disney-earnings-top-estimates-as-cost-cuts-parks-deliver-gains</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 21:05:02 GMT</pubDate>
